&lt;h4&gt;They’ve changed reporting.&lt;/h4&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;The challenge with AI features for marketers isn‘t just traffic, however; it’s also attribution.&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;Organic click-through rates (CTR) have &lt;a href="https://searchengineland.com/zero-click-searche...

&lt;p&gt;AI-referred traffic has increased by &lt;a href="https://www.quantummetric.com/resources/2025-peak-season-benchmark"&gt;600%&lt;/a&gt; since January 2025, and marketers are racing to understand what that means for brand discovery. For teams seeking clarity on how AI impacts brand and pipeline means investing in new tools like Profound or Athena AI for Answer Engine Optimization (AEO). &lt;a class="cta_button" href="https://www.hubspot.com/cs/ci/?pg=d4233c10-60b6-46d7-9852-c71dde8507b6&amp;amp;pid=53&amp;amp;ecid=&amp;amp;hseid=&amp;amp;hsic="&gt;&lt;img class="hs-cta-img " style="height: auto !important; width: auto !important; max-width: 100% !important;border-width: 0px; /*hs-extra-styles*/; " alt="Free AEO Grader: See How You Rank on AI Search Results" height="58" width="529" src="https://no-cache.hubspot.com/cta/default/53/d4233c10-60b6-46d7-9852-c71dde8507b6.png"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;This guide provides a comprehensive comparison between Profound and AthenaHQ, covering what each platform does and how they differ in practice. For SEO strategists building out a new &lt;a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/answer-engine-optimization-best-practices"&gt;AEO practice&lt;/a&gt;, marketing ops leaders evaluating &lt;a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/answer-engine-optimization-tools"&gt;AI search tooling&lt;/a&gt;, or agencies scaling visibility programs across multiple clients, this comparison breaks down which tool fits which growth stack.&lt;/p&gt; 
